<topic id="pntc">
    <title>Percent Number Tones Correct (PNTC)</title>
    <body>
        <p>The Percent Nubmer Tones Correct (PNTC) analysis will calculate the percentage of
            syllables with correctly produced tones in the sampled data. To review how tone numbers
            are specified in Phon please see <xref
                href="../ipa/transcription.dita#phone/tone_number"/>.</p>
    </body>
    <topic id="data-preparation">
        <title>Data Preparation</title>
        <body>
            <p>Session data is queried by word for each IPA Target and IPA Actual tuple. Proper
                syllabification and phone alignment is required for accurate results. All
                participants should have unique names/identification numbers and a speaker should be
                assigned to all records.</p>
        </body>
    </topic>
