    <topic id="topic_wgv_ybb_mjb">
        <title>PNTC Calculation</title>
        <body>
            <p>PNTC is calculated using the following equation:</p>
            <p><foreign outputclass="embed-latex">
                \begin{align} 
                PNTC &amp;= \frac{correct}{(correct + incorrect)} \times 100 \\
                    &amp;= \frac{correct}{(correct + deletions + substitutions)} \times 100
                \end{align}</foreign></p>
        </body>
